examples.explanation:
MinStack minStack = new MinStack();  
- minStack.push(-2);  
- minStack.push(0);  
- minStack.push(-3);  
- minStack.getMin(); // returns -3  
- minStack.pop();  
- minStack.top(); // returns 0  
- minStack.getMin(); // returns -2  


Example 2:

MinStack minStack = new MinStack();  
- minStack.push(5);  
- minStack.push(1);  
- minStack.getMin(); // returns 1  
- minStack.push(3);  
- minStack.pop();  
- minStack.getMin(); // returns 1  
- minStack.top(); // returns 1
